lopment of socialist realism. Deeply researched and lucidly written, this book is a major contribution to the literature on Soviet culture and society.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCommunism and culturezSoviet UnionxHistory. 0aPress and propagandazSoviet UnionxHistory. 0aSocialist realismxHistory. 7aHISTORY / Russia & the Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999z978311044221240uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/9780674040083?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674040083423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674040083/original  a978-3-11-044221-2  HUP eBook Package Archive 1893-1999c1893d1999  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK